      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;salty&#34;&gt;Salty&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This challenge was solved 148 times and it was worth 357 points.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Description:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You might need this: 1337&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Hash: 5eaff45e09bec5222a9cfa9502a4740d&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;NOTE: The flag is NOT in the standard auctf{} format&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The hash seems a salted &lt;code&gt;MD5&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The correct hash mode is &lt;code&gt;md5($salt.$pass)&lt;/code&gt;. So with hashcat:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ hashcat -a &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; -m &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt; salty rockyou.txt&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;.....&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;5eaff45e09bec5222a9cfa9502a4740d:1337:treetop&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;.....&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.raffaeleflorio.com/ctf/auctf2020/images/salty-solved.png&#34; alt=&#34;salty solved banner&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;crack-me-2&#34;&gt;Crack Me 2&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This challenge was solved 108 times and it was worth 880 points.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
